Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二堂课  \NTHE  自习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才不是说明了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢的人要打对方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分哦  好过分的态度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上比打我还过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？  就像刚才说明的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输的话就防御  赢的话就打人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}击碎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在啦  为什么现在打呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我刚才赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在  那是刚才啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在当下  活在当下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是那样的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃喵
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就重新来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲为零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丑啊  就像小丑一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神受到打击了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下  麻衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你要…干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挖到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  这一定是转世再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个放这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得她很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那种东西怎样都好  来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻衣  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}决定一击！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是石剪布啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么如此残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算不算  不准出石剪布啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不准用佛像打人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}盖斯科因！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  来吧  先出石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头·剪刀·布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  就是那样哦  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做还是做得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  先出石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOD  IS  DEAD！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  为什么又要打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  刚才不是玩得很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是觉得不想玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我看看弥勒菩萨吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我去图书馆还书了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好地看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.13,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N21
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}冰箱上：不可以吃太多冰激凌和果汁哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么名乃的不倒翁只有一只眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要是博士把眼睛画上去的话  说不定会表扬我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃也许会说「你吃一堆点心也没关系哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像有点画歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是名乃的  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也许会惹她生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不准博士吃零食！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这样画  这样画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本  怎么办啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥  你这家伙都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那小姑娘的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它没有眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  你就照我说的试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  阪本先生你要出门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要选新借的书所以回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  你那肚子是怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  诶嘿嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是诶嘿嘿啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  没有那种可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要生了啦！  我要生了  我要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那个  你这是在玩什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  名乃的弟弟要诞生啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:29.45,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,240)\fad(600,0)}钱\N仙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩钱仙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美绪居然不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我稍微说明一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在正中画一个鸟居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后写上「是」与「否」和五十音图  就准备这样的一张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:55.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}钱仙又叫狐狗狸，油炸豆腐据说是其喜欢的食物。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然根据地域不同  也有说在纸上写上油炸豆腐会比较好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就按最简单的来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让钱仙进来  要打开北边的门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把这枚10円硬币放在这个鸟居的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起压住硬币  然后问想问的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的秘密之类的  喜欢的人的事情之类的  苦恼着的事情之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话明明什么都没做  10円硬币一下子动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱仙就会做出回答哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先不能一个人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能以开玩笑的心态去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则会被低级灵附身的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  在途中停止的话也会被附身的  要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉  还算是蛮危险的游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  总之开始玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.72,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N22
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天的课就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要进行小考  大家回去要好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  推迟啦推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无论怎么推迟结果都是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  相生同学  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些想问的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是关于前一阵小考的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这题是FLY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是问答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里指勇者斗恶龙里面的消失咒「ニフラム」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看上去好像被下了消失咒的是老师画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得在考试中加入图片能让考试变得更加灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师画的画真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不是很擅长画画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目很难看懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师  下次就用我画的画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会画得超帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说听说我  我画的画会出在小考上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说了「会用我画的画」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪你现在画的话也许也会出在卷子上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说会出  那也有不会出的可能性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  你不画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就算了  不必了  我还得去还这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  那我就画一个超帅的帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的好帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学真会画画呢  佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  其实我就是画得…那么好啦  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一下画的名字叫做「梅雨下的乔治」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  感觉更加帅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫帅！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般被称作帅的应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:23.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害  好像漫画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长野原同学  你有在画漫画吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  嘛  只是稍微画画啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  下次让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看  让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我画的比你更帅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是抄袭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可不是抄袭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抄袭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是名为抄袭的致敬！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这根本就是承认了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都说帅的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这样画的话怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种充满知性的冷酷形象  无论在哪个时代都是女性憧憬的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他视力不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是戴上隐形眼镜的话或许更好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙简直完全不懂嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样画！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜戴到耳朵下面了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这也是抄袭我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧啧  这可是太阳眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没有下限吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这样画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从出门迎接到红茶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你大小姐般的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受大吉岭红茶的魔力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不是很懂这方面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼  不听隐形眼镜的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪你根本就不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  真正的帅指的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唰唰唰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮在空中！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子在开动！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像很快  好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常识上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以常识来考虑的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说帅的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个样子的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:16.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}15:40  1-Q讲台前  长野原美绪  击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边听着爵士乐一边画了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:41.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老湿  早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是老湿啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我现在开始分发早上的小考试卷  请传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是失败  画画这件事本来我想保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然画出了那样的画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  嘛  尽管我暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只画到了那种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是不幸中之万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能不去想最坏的状况了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这两三天就得接受祐子的嘲笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  我得振作  继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪老湿快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  考试开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪老湿～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  咻  啊哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  初次见面  我是拟声词
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜噜噜噜是不想说的日语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是什么日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的日常是第六话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
